## <a id='limitations'></a> Limitation

<%= vars.product_full %> has the following limitations:

* <%= vars.product_short %> is not supported on VMware NSX-T.

* Pivotal recommends configuring <%= vars.product_short %> to use a self-signed certificate to sign instance certificates.
  Pivotal does not recommend using a certificate signed by a public or third-party CA.

* <%= vars.product_short %> is not supported on Windows.
